    "content": "[timestamp:2026-02-11T21:47:02.751Z] 🔧 Tool: Task\nInput: {\n  \"description\": \"Explore deploy and file browser code\",\n  \"subagent_type\": \"Explore\",\n  \"prompt\": \"I need to understand the deploy feature's file/script selection mechanism. Specifically:\\n\\n1. Find all deploy-related components in apps/ui/src/ - especially anything related to selecting a deploy script\\n2. Find the file browser dialog component and understand how it works - look at apps/ui/src/components/dialogs/file-browser-dialog.tsx\\n3. Find the deploy settings/configuration UI where the deploy script path is configured\\n4. Look at apps/ui/src/contexts/file-browser-context.tsx to understand file browser context\\n5. Check the deploy panel component and deploy settings views\\n6. Find the server-side browse route at apps/server/src/routes/fs/routes/browse.ts\\n\\nI need to understand:\\n- How the file browser dialog currently works (does it support file selection vs folder selection?)\\n- How the deploy feature calls the file browser\\n- What mode the file browser is being opened in for deploy script selection\\n- The full flow from deploy settings UI → file browser dialog → file selection\\n\\nBe very thorough - read all relevant files completely.\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-11T21:47:05.191Z] 🔧 Tool: Glob\nInput: {\n  \"pattern\": \"apps/ui/src/components/dialogs/file-browser-dialog.tsx\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-11T21:47:05.338Z] 🔧 Tool: Glob\nInput: {\n  \"pattern\": \"apps/ui/src/contexts/file-browser-context.tsx\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-11T21:47:05.549Z] 🔧 Tool: Glob\nInput: {\n  \"pattern\": \"apps/ui/src/components/views/settings-view/deploy/**\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-11T21:47:05.803Z] 🔧 Tool: Glob\nInput: {\n  \"pattern\": \"apps/ui/src/components/views/board-view/components/deploy-panel.tsx\"\n}\n\n[timestamp:2026-02-11T21:47:06.280Z] 🔧 Tool: Read\nInput: {\n  \"file_path\": \"C:\\\\Users\\\\DylanSmart\\\\Downloads\\\\automaker-pr\\\\apps\\\\ui\\\\src\\\\co